title: Bobby Bones & The Raging Idiots Drop New Song + Dierks Bentley Stops By
itunes:title: Bobby Bones & The Raging Idiots Drop New Song + Dierks Bentley Stops By
description:
Bobby Bones & The Raging Idiots just dropped "The Emoji Love Song," a catchy song about using love songs when it comes to relationships. Also, Dierks Bentley stops by to talk about his new single “Living” and talks about losing an engine while flying a plane.
